[The weekly update basically confirms that WPV1 is still circulating in Afghanistan and Pakistan, and cVDPV2 is still circulating in Niger. It is too soon to definitively state that the viruses are not still circulating in Nigeria, Somalia, the DRC, and Papua New Guinea.

For a map showing the locations of cases of WPV and cVDPV, see http://polioeradication.org/polio-today/polio-now/.

